uientry.s:
local utils = require "Utilities" local this = UIComponent( Address ) local window = UIComponent( UIComponent( this:Parent( "tab_prestige_tracker" ) ):Find( "line_graph_window" ) ) local states = { "tx_overall_ranking", "tx_enlightenment", "tx_military", "tx_naval", "tx_economics" }
function EMBEDDED_RankingFilterForward()
local state = this:CurrentState()
for i=1, #states do
if state == states[ i ] then
if i < #states then
this:SetState( states[ i + 1 ] )
else
this:SetState( states[ 1 ] )
end
end
end
window:LuaCall( "RankingFilterReset", this:CurrentState() )
end
function EMBEDDED_RankingFilterBack()
local state = this:CurrentState()
for i=1, #states do
if state == states[ i ] then
if i ~= 1 then
this:SetState( states[ i - 1 ] )
else
this:SetState( states[ #states ] )
end
end
end
window:LuaCall( "RankingFilterReset", this:CurrentState() )
end
